Package: easyicer
Title: Set of functions for easy computation and plotting of ICERs
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Brendan", "Chia", , "bchia1212@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This R package contains 3 functions: `summed_output()`, `icercalc`, and `icerplot` which together can be used to sum numeric columns to obtain ICER inputs, calculate and plot ICERs. This package contains multiple dependencies to support syntax compatibility and plotting.
